item.title: Help with installing java somethings wrong
item.dc:creator: @owned654321241 owned654321241
item.description:
@owned654321241 wrote:

ok look…

  1. Download the latest version of jdk off the java website

then

  1. Replace the code in your compiler with this…

@echo off Title (YOUR SERVER NAME HERE) Compiler "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_13\bin\javac.exe" *.java pause

and replace the words (YOUR SERVER NAME HERE) with your server name.

And you should be set.
